<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

5
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

6
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:34,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa benar mereka ibu dan anakmu
sebelum kau aku kebiri?</font>

7
00:00:34,969 --> 00:00:36,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu.</font>

8
00:00:36,539 --> 00:00:38,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong... tolong
selamatkan nyawa mereka.</font>

9
00:00:38,870 --> 00:00:42,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir aku tidak tahu
kau memata-mataiku?</font>

10
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:46,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menceritakan semuanya.
Aku harus mulai dari mana?</font>

11
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:50,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mau susah-susah bertanya.</font>

12
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:52,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kebiri anaknya seperti Ayahnya.</font>

13
00:00:54,190 --> 00:00:58,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak hanya mengejar
harta Menteri Keuangan.</font>

14
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:01,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika neneknya melihat, dia mungkin sangat
terkejut, jadi tunjukkan belas kasihan...</font>

15
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:03,400
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan membutakan mata ibunya.</font>

16
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka ingin mengangkat Wang Lin.</font>

17
00:01:07,270 --> 00:01:09,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena Wang Lin menyukai putrinya,</font>

18
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:12,669
<font color=#FFFF00>...mereka mencoba
untuk menikahinya, Ratu!</font>

19
00:01:16,409 --> 00:01:19,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa orang yang kau bilang "mereka"?</font>

20
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:27,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengikut Pangeran
Gang Yang, Ratu!</font>

21
00:01:34,490 --> 00:01:36,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Wang Lin dan bukan Wang Jeon?</font>

22
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:41,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong lepaskan dia. Tolong
lepaskan Ibuku, Ratu.</font>

23
00:01:43,469 --> 00:01:45,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa mereka mengejar Wang Lin?</font>

24
00:01:50,380 --> 00:01:52,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menunggu
saat yang tepat.</font>

25
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:57,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena tinggal bersama
Seja Jeoha adalah tempat teraman,</font>

26
00:01:58,019 --> 00:01:59,990
<font color=#FFFF00>...mereka membiarkannya dan menunggu...</font>

27
00:02:03,189 --> 00:02:06,230
<font color=#FFFF00>...sampai Tuan Lin tumbuh dewasa.</font>

28
00:02:37,820 --> 00:02:40,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha./
Tidak, lepaskan aku.</font>

29
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:42,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sangat mahal.
Aku akan menuangnya sendiri.</font>

30
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:52,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, lihat./
Iya.</font>

31
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:54,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini seolloju.</font>

32
00:02:57,339 --> 00:03:00,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu Yangonseo
kita punya ini.</font>

33
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:01,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

34
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa banyak botol disana?</font>

35
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,950
<font color=#FFFF00>13 botol.</font>

36
00:03:06,950 --> 00:03:08,649
<font color=#FFFF00>13 botol.</font>

37
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebanyak itu?</font>

38
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

39
00:03:18,730 --> 00:03:19,899
<font color=#FFFF00>...harus...</font>

40
00:03:21,799 --> 00:03:24,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...memanjat gunung itu karena
minuman keras ini...</font>

41
00:03:25,739 --> 00:03:27,709
<font color=#FFFF00>...dalam hujan deras.</font>

42
00:03:31,709 --> 00:03:33,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bersama Lin...</font>

43
00:03:34,510 --> 00:03:36,320
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan So Ah.</font>

44
00:03:45,459 --> 00:03:48,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi setidaknya kami
bersama-sama saat itu.</font>

45
00:03:51,230 --> 00:03:52,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersama-sama.</font>

46
00:04:05,709 --> 00:04:06,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu?</font>

47
00:04:08,510 --> 00:04:12,049
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir bisa berhenti
memikirkan mereka jika mabuk.</font>

48
00:04:12,589 --> 00:04:14,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi mengapa aku
semakin memikirkannya?</font>

49
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:20,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu telah menginterogasi
Choi Se Yeon.</font>

50
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:23,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin bersama Menteri
Keuangan dan Nona San.</font>

51
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Beri aku waktu sebentar.</font>

52
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar.</font>

53
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:41,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda akan pergi?
Bagaimana dengan Nona San?</font>

54
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:43,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada hal yang harus aku urus.
Aku akan kembali.</font>

55
00:04:43,349 --> 00:04:45,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda akan kembali?</font>

56
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah anda kembali malam hari ini?</font>

57
00:04:47,149 --> 00:04:48,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan kembali sebelum fajar.</font>

58
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa.</font>

59
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

60
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa mengemasi
barang Nona San?</font>

61
00:05:08,339 --> 00:05:10,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Berkemas?/
Supaya dia bisa pergi kapanpun.</font>

62
00:05:11,779 --> 00:05:13,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menyusahkannya.</font>

63
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:15,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mohon.</font>

64
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:31,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak percaya ini.</font>

65
00:05:33,599 --> 00:05:36,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa Menteri Keuangan
meninggal seperti itu?</font>

66
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:39,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia sungguh ingin bertemu dengan Ayah?</font>

67
00:05:40,909 --> 00:05:43,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar./ Apa dia di sini untuk
membicarakan pernikahan?</font>

68
00:05:45,579 --> 00:05:46,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

69
00:05:47,349 --> 00:05:49,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Pernikahan antara kau
dan putrinya.</font>

70
00:05:49,479 --> 00:05:51,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Ayah yakin...</font>

71
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:55,050
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk aku, bukannya Hyungnim?</font>

72
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

73
00:05:57,389 --> 00:06:02,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang kesehatannya sedang memburuk,
dan dia khawatir pada putrinya.</font>

74
00:06:03,099 --> 00:06:06,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia sangat berharap dariku.</font>

75
00:06:07,099 --> 00:06:08,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pikir kau bisa dipercaya.</font>

76
00:06:10,269 --> 00:06:12,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin kau menjaga putrinya.</font>

77
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:18,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika benar Ratu melakukan
itu pada Menteri Keuangan,</font>

78
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:25,050
<font color=#FFFF00>...itu artinya masa depan putrinya tidak
akan aman.</font>

79
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berencana untuk
pergi bersama Nona San.</font>

80
00:06:36,229 --> 00:06:37,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau melepaskan gelarmu...</font>

81
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,370
<font color=#FFFF00>...sebagai Inspektur Jenderal?</font>

82
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

83
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:44,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan jadi buronan.</font>

84
00:06:45,909 --> 00:06:48,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya./
Apa kau mengatakan...</font>

85
00:06:49,139 --> 00:06:51,579
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan menyia-nyiakan
sisa hidupmu?</font>

86
00:06:52,579 --> 00:06:54,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena dia?</font>

87
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:59,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu-satunya hal yang aku
khawatirkan adalah keluarga kita.</font>

88
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:03,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Keluarga kita akan terluka
karena aku, tapi...</font>

89
00:07:03,589 --> 00:07:04,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Lin.</font>

90
00:07:08,529 --> 00:07:10,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku, Ayah.</font>

91
00:07:12,130 --> 00:07:14,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa memikirkan
cara lain.</font>

92
00:07:15,329 --> 00:07:17,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Seja Jeoha tahu?</font>

93
00:07:34,789 --> 00:07:36,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokumen...</font>

94
00:07:37,089 --> 00:07:39,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang kita ambil dari San...</font>

95
00:07:56,610 --> 00:07:57,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, ini.</font>

96
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,579
<font color=#FFFF00>Gandumnya.</font>

97
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:04,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukan dengan benar.</font>

98
00:08:04,019 --> 00:08:07,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu. Anda harus istirahat hari ini...</font>

99
00:08:07,089 --> 00:08:08,789
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan memikirkannya besok.</font>

100
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak banyak waktu.</font>

101
00:08:11,459 --> 00:08:13,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Anakku sedang berdiri di dekat tebing.</font>

102
00:08:14,690 --> 00:08:16,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Sedikit waktu bagiku.</font>

103
00:08:27,969 --> 00:08:29,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka menunggu waktu yang tepat.</font>

104
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:32,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka membiarkan dia dekat denganku
di tempat yang paling aman...</font>

105
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,279
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menunggu sampai dia dewasa.</font>

106
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:39,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu yang dia katakan./
Itu bohong.</font>

107
00:08:39,089 --> 00:08:40,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Selain Pangeran Gang Yang,</font>

108
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:43,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia akan menjadi Raja.</font>

109
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:45,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu omong kosong./
Itu benar.</font>

110
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia temanku.</font>

111
00:08:56,099 --> 00:08:59,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah memberi tahu penjaga?/
Semua orang yang bertugas telah diberitahu.</font>

112
00:09:00,009 --> 00:09:03,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Tuan Lin datang,
dia akan dibawa ke sini.</font>

113
00:09:03,239 --> 00:09:05,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia akan datang?
Ini sudah larut malam.</font>

114
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:06,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan datang.</font>

115
00:09:08,109 --> 00:09:10,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Banyak hal yang harus dia katakan padaku.</font>

116
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:14,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak akan menunggu sampai pagi.</font>

117
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak cocok dengan namanya.</font>

118
00:09:22,229 --> 00:09:23,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

119
00:09:25,229 --> 00:09:26,700
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Wine</i> ini.</font>

120
00:09:28,499 --> 00:09:30,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meminum semuanya,
dan aku belum mabuk.</font>

121
00:09:32,770 --> 00:09:34,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikiranku masih jernih.</font>

122
00:09:35,609 --> 00:09:37,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pasti <i>wine</i> palsu.</font>

123
00:09:40,709 --> 00:09:42,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harusnya datang lebih cepat.</font>

124
00:09:44,180 --> 00:09:45,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Bodoh sekali.</font>

125
00:10:17,749 --> 00:10:19,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku datang untuk menyelesaikan...</font>

126
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,650
<font color=#FFFF00>...percakapan kita tadi.</font>

127
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:51,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami telah menunggu, dan percaya
kau akan kembali.</font>

128
00:10:51,979 --> 00:10:53,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya beberapa pertanyaan.</font>

129
00:10:53,719 --> 00:10:55,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau boleh bertanya.</font>

130
00:10:55,420 --> 00:10:59,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau membiarkanku
menemui Pangeran Gang Yang?</font>

131
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:01,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengungkapkan kebenaran padamu.</font>

132
00:11:01,129 --> 00:11:02,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk apa?</font>

133
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:05,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk memintamu,
bangsawan berdarah murni,</font>

134
00:11:05,999 --> 00:11:07,300
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengambil tahtanya.</font>

135
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau berencana untuk memberontak?</font>

136
00:11:09,969 --> 00:11:13,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat muak dengan itu.</font>

137
00:11:13,469 --> 00:11:16,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadilah Pangeran Mahkota.</font>

138
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:22,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kembali, karena percaya...</font>

139
00:11:22,849 --> 00:11:26,020
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan membunuhmu, itu akan menguntungkan
Seja Jeoha-ku.</font>

140
00:11:27,349 --> 00:11:29,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa ada beberapa orang lagi.</font>

141
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:32,560
<font color=#FFFF00>2 lebih baik dari 1, dan
3 lebih baik dari 2.</font>

142
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:35,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Semakin banyak aku membunuh,
itu semakin baik.</font>

143
00:11:35,629 --> 00:11:37,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin./
Keluarkan pedangmu.</font>

144
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:39,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita...</font>

145
00:11:39,829 --> 00:11:41,170
<font color=#FFFF00>...berada dipihak yang sama.</font>

146
00:11:42,469 --> 00:11:43,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau...</font>

147
00:11:44,170 --> 00:11:45,339
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau mau mati.</font>

148
00:12:08,989 --> 00:12:12,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat datang, Tuan Lin./
Selamat datang, Tuan Lin.</font>

149
00:12:20,570 --> 00:12:23,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat datang, Tuan Lin./
Selamat datang, Tuan Lin.</font>

150
00:12:38,190 --> 00:12:40,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Goryeo yang hebat...</font>

151
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,999
<font color=#FFFF00>...harus bebas dari Yuan.</font>

152
00:12:42,999 --> 00:12:45,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami hanya ingin melayani Kerajaan saja.</font>

153
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:49,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang-orang setia ini
menunggu hari itu.</font>

154
00:12:52,369 --> 00:12:55,709
<font color=#FFFF00>"Goryeo yang hebat"?
"Darah murni"?</font>

155
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:59,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong kosong.
Apa kau menggunakan itu...</font>

156
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,849
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk memisahkan Raja dan
anaknya...</font>

157
00:13:01,849 --> 00:13:03,780
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan demi keserakahanmu sendiri?</font>

158
00:13:06,489 --> 00:13:08,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama aku masih hidup,</font>

159
00:13:09,359 --> 00:13:11,459
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan menemukan dan melenyapkan
kalian satu persatu.</font>

160
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:15,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menghilangkan
hama Goryeo sepertimu.</font>

161
00:13:40,290 --> 00:13:42,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Ra... Ra...</font>

162
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:45,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja.</font>

163
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

164
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:51,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku, Rajamu.</font>

165
00:14:47,989 --> 00:14:50,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lihat?/
Siapa yang menembaknya?</font>

166
00:14:51,989 --> 00:14:54,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa tulisannya? Ini.</font>

167
00:14:58,759 --> 00:15:00,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha. Jeoha.</font>

168
00:15:02,499 --> 00:15:04,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha, para
Komandan ada di sini.</font>

169
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:09,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Joeha./
<i>Seja Jeoha.</i></font>

170
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:12,339
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku Ko Sung dari Tentara Eungyang.</i></font>

171
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:16,749
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku Lim Chi Young dari
Tentara Yongho.</i></font>

172
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:18,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangun.</font>

173
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:22,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha, bangunlah.</font>

174
00:15:26,060 --> 00:15:28,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Lama tak jumpa, Para Komandan.</font>

175
00:15:33,369 --> 00:15:36,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kita ada jadwal bertemu?</font>

176
00:15:39,369 --> 00:15:42,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menerima catatan tanpa nama./
Aku tahu.</font>

177
00:15:44,810 --> 00:15:46,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah biasa jika tanpa nama.</font>

178
00:15:46,650 --> 00:15:49,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Gandum yang hilang dari
ruang penyimpanan kita...</font>

179
00:15:49,650 --> 00:15:50,950
<font color=#FFFF00>...sudah ditemukan.</font>

180
00:15:56,359 --> 00:15:57,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana?</font>

181
00:15:57,520 --> 00:16:00,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau siapa?
Minggir!</font>

182
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:06,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menemukannya di
gudang Eun Young Baek.</font>

183
00:16:07,430 --> 00:16:09,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka dicap dengan segel kita.</font>

184
00:16:10,170 --> 00:16:13,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua karung gandum di sana,</font>

185
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:16,079
<font color=#FFFF00>...memiliki tanda ini.</font>

186
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:21,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami juga menemukan ruang penyimpanan
dengan tanda yang sama...</font>

187
00:16:21,079 --> 00:16:23,820
<font color=#FFFF00>...di tempat lain./
Dimana?</font>

188
00:16:26,890 --> 00:16:29,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Rumah Kanselir Wang Yeong.</font>

189
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Catatan tanpa nama.</font>

190
00:16:36,099 --> 00:16:38,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa disitu tertulis untuk mencari...</font>

191
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:41,570
<font color=#FFFF00>...gandum yang hilang di rumah Kanselir?</font>

192
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:44,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menemukan bukti
konkret di rumah Tuan Eun.</font>

193
00:16:47,940 --> 00:16:49,239
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kami,</i></font>

194
00:16:49,239 --> 00:16:52,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...menemukan sejumlah
besar biji-bijian...</i></font>

195
00:16:52,140 --> 00:16:56,450
<font color=#FFFF00>...sudah sering dikirim ke
rumah Kanselir sebelumnya.</font>

196
00:17:02,349 --> 00:17:05,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu Anda
berteman dekat dengan...</font>

197
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:06,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...putra Kanselir.</font>

198
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:09,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun.../
Jangan memihak?</font>

199
00:17:09,459 --> 00:17:12,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Menghukum mereka dengan adil?/
Benar.</font>

200
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:14,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menyuruh pengawal
mengawasi rumah Kanselir.</font>

201
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:18,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi tidak ada yang melarikan
diri sebelum mereka dihukum.</font>

202
00:17:18,340 --> 00:17:20,569
<font color=#FFFF00>Tampaknya Tuan Lin
telah melarikan diri.</font>

203
00:17:20,809 --> 00:17:24,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami tidak menemukannya
sejak dia kesini.</font>

204
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kami harus menangkapnya?</font>

205
00:17:28,209 --> 00:17:30,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Lain masalahnya dengan Tuan Eun.</font>

206
00:17:31,779 --> 00:17:33,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tiba-tiba meninggal.</font>

207
00:17:34,090 --> 00:17:36,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia punya putri dan tidak punya putra,</font>

208
00:17:36,519 --> 00:17:39,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kami harus membawanya?/
Apa kami membiarkan dia menyelesaikan pemakaman?</font>

209
00:18:21,930 --> 00:18:23,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Tandu jenazahnya sudah siap.</font>

210
00:18:26,940 --> 00:18:28,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus melihatnya pergi.</font>

211
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:31,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

212
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingat ini.</font>

213
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:37,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu hanya menginginkan satu hal.</font>

214
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Keselamatanmu.</font>

215
00:18:45,190 --> 00:18:46,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu.</font>

216
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:49,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu semuanya akan
baik-baik saja.</font>

217
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada kabar dari Lin?</font>

218
00:19:11,180 --> 00:19:12,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Belum.</font>

219
00:19:18,390 --> 00:19:20,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita tunggu sebentar lagi.</font>

220
00:19:21,259 --> 00:19:24,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Lin dan San akan pergi
ke prosesi pemakaman.</font>

221
00:19:25,229 --> 00:19:27,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan biarkan satupun
dari mereka pergi.</font>

222
00:19:28,569 --> 00:19:30,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa mereka sebelum
Seja tahu.</font>

223
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:32,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika mereka melawan,</font>

224
00:19:35,739 --> 00:19:37,209
<font color=#FFFF00>...bunuh mereka.</font>

225
00:19:39,450 --> 00:19:40,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir!</font>

226
00:19:41,249 --> 00:19:43,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir./
Minggir!</font>

227
00:19:45,749 --> 00:19:48,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Jelas sekali apa yang
akan dilakukan Ratu.</font>

228
00:19:49,219 --> 00:19:53,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa Lin padaku dengan aman.
Mereka tidak bisa menyentuh rambutnya sekalipun.</font>

229
00:19:54,959 --> 00:19:58,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan segera menjadi
Putra Mahkota.</font>

230
00:20:11,309 --> 00:20:12,509
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Eun San.</i></font>

231
00:20:13,309 --> 00:20:14,709
<font color=#FFFF00><i>So Ah-ku.</i></font>

232
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku minta maaf...</i></font>

233
00:20:18,719 --> 00:20:20,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak bisa berada di sana
untuk melihat Ayahmu pergi.</i></font>

234
00:20:22,019 --> 00:20:24,759
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada saat dimana aku harus...</i></font>

235
00:20:25,559 --> 00:20:28,059
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...memilih antara kau dan Lin.</i></font>

236
00:20:29,059 --> 00:20:32,700
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pada saat itu, aku memilihmu tanpa ragu.</i></font>

237
00:20:36,170 --> 00:20:39,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Apamama bilang akan melepaskan...</font>

238
00:20:40,269 --> 00:20:42,440
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau atau So Ah.</font>

239
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:45,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku atau So Ah?</font>

240
00:20:45,479 --> 00:20:46,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi...</font>

241
00:20:47,549 --> 00:20:49,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memilih So Ah.</font>

242
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan...</font>

243
00:20:52,650 --> 00:20:54,019
<font color=#FFFF00>...meninggalkanmu disini.</font>

244
00:20:55,049 --> 00:20:57,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahan melihat dia...</font>

245
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:01,630
<font color=#FFFF00>...dipukul dan diseret.</font>

246
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah alasannya.</font>

247
00:21:06,670 --> 00:21:08,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang aku satu-satunya temanmu...</font>

248
00:21:09,870 --> 00:21:12,610
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan satu-satunya
orang yang bisa kau percaya.</font>

249
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:14,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

250
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:18,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kau akan meninggalkanku di sini...</font>

251
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:21,680
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menyelamatkan seorang wanita?</font>

252
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

253
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:38,029
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kali ini, aku akan
memilih Lin daripada dirimu.</i></font>

254
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:45,170
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bisakah kau tersenyum...</i></font>

255
00:21:45,469 --> 00:21:47,769
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan menerimanya seperti yang
dilakukan Lin saat itu?</i></font>

256
00:21:50,709 --> 00:21:52,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menerima perintah kerajaan.</font>

257
00:21:56,319 --> 00:21:58,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Wang Dan, keturunan bangsawan dan...</font>

258
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:01,620
<font color=#FFFF00>...putri Kanselir Wang Yeong,</font>

259
00:22:02,190 --> 00:22:04,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...dipilih menjadi calon pengantin
Seja.</font>

260
00:22:05,390 --> 00:22:09,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus datang ke istana dan
bersiap untuk menikah.</font>

261
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:30,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangkat-pangkat ini akan diberikan
sebelum pernikahan Seja Jeoha.</font>

262
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:34,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Wang Yeong akan menjadi Seowonok,
Wang Bu akan menjadi Ikyanghu,</font>

263
00:22:34,420 --> 00:22:36,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Wang Jeon akan menjadi Seoheunghu,</font>

264
00:22:36,259 --> 00:22:39,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan Wang Lin akan menjadi Sujeong,
jadi jangan sampai ada kesalahan.</font>

265
00:22:39,930 --> 00:22:42,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Pernikahan akan dilakukan dua hari lagi.</font>

266
00:22:42,190 --> 00:22:43,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Dua hari?/
Cepat sekali?</font>

267
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:46,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Keluarga dari calon Putri
Mahkota...</font>

268
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:50,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak bisa dikenakan hukuman apapun
selain pengkhianatan.</font>

269
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:52,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu yang harus kalian ketahui.</font>

270
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:54,039
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kita harus protes./
Tidak.</i></font>

271
00:22:54,569 --> 00:22:56,279
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa yang terjadi?/
Aneh sekali.</i></font>

272
00:22:56,279 --> 00:22:57,910
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa ini masuk akal?</i></font>

273
00:23:05,049 --> 00:23:08,690
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau ingat apa yang
pernah kau katakan padaku?</i></font>

274
00:23:12,289 --> 00:23:13,459
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ambil ini.</i></font>

275
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:15,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini peninggalan Ibuku.</font>

276
00:23:16,630 --> 00:23:18,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa menerimanya.
Itu terlalu berharga.</font>

277
00:23:18,759 --> 00:23:21,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tanda janji./
Janji?</font>

278
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:22,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika nanti,</font>

279
00:23:24,039 --> 00:23:26,739
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau ingin meminta bantuanku,
tunjukkan ini.</font>

280
00:23:28,569 --> 00:23:30,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu aku akan
memberimu apa saja.</font>

281
00:24:17,489 --> 00:24:19,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lalu kau ingat apa yang
aku katakan padamu?</i></font>

282
00:24:21,259 --> 00:24:24,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Selalu, sampai kapanpun,</i></font>

283
00:24:26,029 --> 00:24:27,900
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kau akan menjadi yang pertama.</i></font>

284
00:24:29,299 --> 00:24:30,999
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jangan pernah lupa itu.</i></font>

285
00:24:37,779 --> 00:24:39,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan kepada Nona San.</font>

286
00:24:40,650 --> 00:24:42,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan meminta
untuk bertemu denganku.</font>

287
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:46,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia dengan aman</font>

288
00:25:01,499 --> 00:25:05,239
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tandu jenazah akan lewat.</i></font>

289
00:25:05,239 --> 00:25:10,180
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Buat jalan untuk prosesi pemakaman.</i></font>

290
00:25:10,410 --> 00:25:14,309
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jalan menuju kehidupan selanjutnya.</i></font>

291
00:25:14,749 --> 00:25:18,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sangat panjang dan sulit.</i></font>

292
00:25:18,979 --> 00:25:22,959
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mari kita menuju gunung.</i></font>

293
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:27,229
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu menghadap ke Utara.</i></font>

294
00:25:36,069 --> 00:25:39,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau meninggalkan kehidupan ini.</i></font>

295
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:45,340
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kapan kau akan...</i></font>

296
00:25:45,340 --> 00:25:48,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kembali?/</i>
Minggir.</font>

297
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:51,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus menunggu sampai
mereka meninggalkan kota.</font>

298
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:53,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Eun sangat terkenal.</font>

299
00:25:53,749 --> 00:25:56,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kita membawa putrinya,
mereka akan menyerang kita.</font>

300
00:25:56,319 --> 00:25:58,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah ke tujuan prosesi,
dan tunggu mereka.</font>

301
00:25:59,190 --> 00:26:00,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menggunakan caraku sendiri.</font>

302
00:26:12,170 --> 00:26:14,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangkap dia sebelum mereka
meninggalkan kota.</font>

303
00:26:21,410 --> 00:26:24,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak punya hak dan
kurang percaya diri,</i></font>

304
00:26:25,650 --> 00:26:27,890
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...jadi aku mengandalkan
kekuatan kalung ini.</i></font>

305
00:26:27,989 --> 00:26:33,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Selamat tinggal, aku meninggalkan dunia ini.</i></font>

306
00:26:39,630 --> 00:26:40,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i>San.</i></font>

307
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,900
<font color=#FFFF00><i>So Ah-ku.</i></font>

308
00:26:44,170 --> 00:26:45,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kembalilah.</i></font>

309
00:26:47,209 --> 00:26:48,569
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tetap bersamaku.</i></font>

310
00:26:57,593 --> 00:26:59,993
